:

1. *Komad* hleba je ostao na stolu. (A piece of bread remained on the table.)
2. On je skrenuo sa glavnog puta i ubacio *komad* trave u usta. (He turned off the main road and put a blade of grass in his mouth.)
3. Ona je došla sa niskim *komadom* odeće. (She came with a piece of clothing.)
4. Ona je prekrila stol sa *komadom* platna. (She covered the table with a piece of cloth.)
5. On je ponio *komad* nakita u džepu. (He carried a piece of jewelry in his pocket.)